description: This Chainlink VRF top 15% score Yulenka purrs with a rating of 68, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 136, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Nine Lives for East, Box for South, and Nine Lives for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80682-19494-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [136 Votes, Top 15% Score]
